{
  "stem": "25639.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when daylight broke, my dad looked through the cracks of the cattle cars, and he commented that he did not like what he saw.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He noticed all the electric wire fences and rows and rows and rows of long barracks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The name of the place, as we later learned, was Auschwitz-Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then the doors were shoved open and German voices screamed at us, [GERMAN], or out, out, and further orders were shouted at us to, to, to walk in a certain direction in an orderly fashion.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We arrived four days later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it was-- I don't want to be pinned down to the exact date, if you don't mind, because I know that our trip took four days.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we arrived in, in Auschwitz, and men in striped uniform hopped up into the wagon, into the cattle cars, and bent over pretending to be doing this or that or picking up packages or luggage or bundles that we had along with us, and these men kept whispering to us, you are 16.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You are 14.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You are 15.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Tell them you can do, do work in the fields.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Tell them you were a farmer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Tell them that you can-- you always worked hard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were very confused anyway, and this truly added to our confusion, except that perhaps a little ray of hope, too, because it, it-- as I think about it, it must have made us feel that at least we will be able to work.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that perhaps, if we tell them a certain-- give them a certain bit of information, perhaps they're going to put us in that type of work.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we learned later what this really meant.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
